scripts/__pycache__


# Autocode runtime
.opencode/autopilot/runtime/
.opencode/autopilot/*.sqlite3
.opencode/autopilot/*.db
tmp/autopilot_scratch/
.opencode/autopilot/kpi/*.html
.opencode/autopilot/__pycache__
.opencode/checkpoint_output.json
tests/__pycache__

# Coverage/inspection artifacts
# `coverage.py` (and several editors/tools) emit sibling files with a
# `,cover` suffix or `.cover` extension when serializing annotated source.
# These are operational noise, never source-of-truth, and have been observed
# to leak into scripts/ and tests/ after autopilot runs. See
# tests/test_repo_hygiene.py::test_no_cover_artifacts_in_scripts for the
# regression guard.
*,cover
*.cover
/.coverage
/.coverage.*
graphify-out/